snippet.title: Dustborn | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming early 2024 on PC and consoles! Learn more: 
https://www.quanticdream.com/en/dustborn

Ragtag crew? Check. Musical gear? Check. Tour bus and robot driver? Check. Stolen package? Check! Embark on a perilous road-trip across a Divided States of America. Use the power of words to shape relationships with your crew, get out of trouble and reach your final destination.
• Wishlist now: 
• Subscribe on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/QuanticDreamOfficial
• Subscribe to our newsletter: https://www.quanticdream.com/en/sign-up
